---
layout: default.njk
title: "Bitcoin Guides | CryptoZing"
description: "Plain-language guides on Bitcoin payments, confirmations, invoicing, and more."
canonical: "https://cryptozing.app/learn/"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<style>
  .learn-wrap {
    max-width: var(--prose-max);
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .learn-wrap h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .learn-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
  }

  .article-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .article-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 140ms ease, background 140ms ease;
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .article-card-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .article-card-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>

<div class="learn-wrap">
  <h1>Bitcoin Guides</h1>
  <p class="learn-intro">Plain-language guides on Bitcoin payments, invoicing, and what actually happens on-chain.</p>

  <ul class="article-list">
    {% for post in collections.learn | reverse %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="article-card">
        <p class="article-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</p>
        <p class="article-card-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
